{"tid":2158960,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"渣哥三番四次分化黃店，仲三番四次block人滅聲，仲食佢個d不如食埋美心吉野家啦","createTime":"2020-08-16T04:44:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T07:20:54.000Z","uid":9747,"like":37,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"92f0c0f01649f00738a67afb2972c1e15491c646","tid":2158960,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:44:41.000Z","msg":"渣哥又瀨咗嘢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2158427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2158427</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母你隻渣狗 一間黃店一晚block我3個account？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2158689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2158689</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n渣哥釀成公關災難<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2158361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2158361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美心高層笑香港人，藍店罷食<br />\n吉野家滅員工聲，藍店罷食<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">渣哥笑鳩黃店，分化黃店，屈人強姦，block哂所有反對聲音滅香港人聲</span></span><br />\n渣渣軍：唔好分化黃店啦<br />\n<br />\n如果香港人睇著同路人咁樣比人屌到上心口，連聲都滅埋都照支持呢d店<br />\n仲屌返被滅聲既人係分化撚既話<br />\n咁你不如食撚埋藍店/偽黃店啦<br />\n橫掂你地都係跟風食明星店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞乜野黃圈姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa38f440cfde7da7b5f4a333681f087661173a33","tid":2158960,"uid":9747,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"話人分化黃店個班<br />\n諗下點解香港咁多黃店<br />\n淨係水陸渣呢班會被人屌<br />\n<br />\n諗埋點解龍門比水陸渣狙擊個時<br />\n你地又唔出黎屌佢地分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟邊d人先係分化源頭<br />\n醒目既香港人無理由睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b46fb40520a37d61d192c2c7abaf8063c6626d3","tid":2158960,"uid":9747,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:56:02.000Z","msg":"推到渣哥收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持其他黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\